Create a site with 2 pages.

Requirements

The redirection between the pages will be using buttons. The buttons must be placed on the right center of the pages. It must be coloured (you choice).

Anywhere in the 1st (home) page, place your full name. The first letter of the name and the first letter of the surname must be bold.

The background color of both the pages must be coloured (your choice) but different colours.
